A '''cadet leader''' was a [[Cadet/Legends|cadet]] at the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] academies who was given command over a platoon of troopers and the responsibility for handling a minor military operation as part of the [[Omega Exercise]].

A notable cadet leader was [[Kyle Katarn]] who was responsible for the Imperial victory over [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] forces on [[AX-456]]. Katarn emerged an Imperial hero and was decorated by his enemy-to-be, [[Jerec (Inquisitor)|Jerec]].

